reviewText: Expecting a video on cruising to and from Alaska, I was disappointed to learn that approximately 25% of the video time was spent on the cruise journey and experience, while the remaining 75% was a travel documentary on a variety of sights and excursions in Alaska, namely train rides, helicopter, planes, and even whitewater rafting adventures. The scenery was of course quite beautiful, but the choreography was equivalent to that of which we were once forced to watch in high school, dry and "documentary" styled.
